### ŌÜĀ’ĖÅ Fantasy Projections: No npm Package Exists

There's no npm package that provides fantasy scoring projections natively ŌĆö that data comes from third-party sites. Your best approaches:

| Source           | Strategy                                                                         |
| ---------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **SportsDataIO** | Paid REST API ŌĆö call it directly with `fetch`/`axios`, no npm wrapper needed     |
| **FantasyPros**  | No API; scrape `fantasypros.com/mlb/projections/sp.php` with `cheerio` + `axios` |
| **FanGraphs**    | Export CSVs from their projections pages and parse with `papaparse`              |

